{"tid":1835242,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有冇人諗過酒店同服務業唔比戴口罩啊。可唔可以幫手反映下或投訴","createTime":"2020-01-22T18:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T09:56:38.000Z","uid":133763,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"75a5e8c776e26cb94077987bf76dc9fa08e2cb72","tid":1835242,"uid":133763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:56:18.000Z","msg":"仆街<br />\n<br />\n殺到埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n部份酒店同服務業仲未有指示叫戴口罩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n要顧及專業形象，唔可以令客人受驚</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你唔會知道佢地有冇接觸過武漢人，亦都唔會知道自己係咪潛伏緊嘅帶菌者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實前線嘅服務員好撚慘<br />\n<br />\n作為客人嘅你可唔可以幫手屌屌佢？<br />\n<br />\n從今天起，邊間酒店食肆唔撚戴口罩嘅，直接成間公司投訴（並非針對個別員工）<br />\n<br />\n一人一反映<br />\n<br />\n緊急"},{"pid":"ef0b6ef598856926e0c3d3e9b90f1a24b1645404","tid":1835242,"uid":111996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:57:17.000Z","msg":"美心集團呢？"},{"pid":"228488c98046cf4a19a7054324e87dc154029889","tid":1835242,"uid":133763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef0b6ef598856926e0c3d3e9b90f1a24b1645404","tid":1835242,"uid":111996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:57:17.000Z","msg":"美心集團呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:58:19.000Z","msg":"更加要屌"},{"pid":"c6be45598198cb22e8c24905a8744e6d89625bab","tid":1835242,"uid":122275,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:59:31.000Z","msg":"On9自己戴啦<br />\n唔俾戴咪即刻唔做<br />\n個個都覺得自己可以死好命冇事"},{"pid":"43d5a9d7a02e13b82c47a27458063ea71dbfb2b5","tid":1835242,"uid":133763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6be45598198cb22e8c24905a8744e6d89625bab","tid":1835242,"uid":122275,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:59:31.000Z","msg":"On9自己戴啦<br />\n唔俾戴咪即刻唔做<br />\n個個都覺得自己可以死好命冇事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T19:07:51.000Z","msg":"假設你係食客<br />\n<br />\n會同你接觸嘅就係服務員<br />\n<br />\n佢唔戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n你有冇得避？<br />\n<br />\n除非你咁瀟灑唔幫襯佢"},